Slatter, London, Mai-Juli 1949, N° 2; Hochzeitsprocession: 1) Spencer-Churchchill: Sehr gut in Arundel club. Breughel 1630; [verso] 7) Sale Chillingsworth, Luzern Fischer, 5-IX-1926, N° 14; 8) Sale Osborn Kliny (Stockholm) Christie, 28-6- 1935, N° 13, 271/2 x 41 [?] in. signed and dated 1630, repr.
